  <Summary>Exiled to the Crossroads Dimension, the Hulk comes across the Puffball Collective. Doctor Strange is a close onlooker.

Hulk appears at the centre of Crossroads where he is met with a tree that has a hundred pointing hands. Hulk uproots with a single punch. He then focus' his attention on the Puffball Collective. However, Hulk is unable to fight the onslaught of the Puffball's. The Puffball's try to befriend Hulk by forming into a familiar figure; Bruce Banner. How will the Hulk react? Will Hulk have a new friend or foe?

First issue to feature the Puffball Collective.</Summary>
